text: Sadaif Mehdi (born 14 August 1994) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Multan in the 2013–14 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 23 October 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Multan cricketers Category:United Bank Limited cricketers Category:Water and Power Development Authority cricketers Category:Southern Punjab (Pakistan) cricketers
